# Camtasia Skill share Tutorial Notes

### Use Green Screen Video to Add additional effects

- For example, you can find lot of video on youtube with green screen back ground and you can overlap that with your actual video, This will create lot of cool possibility

### Separate Video and audio

- So camtasia has inbuild feature to separate audio and video for further editing, Just right click on your footage in timeline and that option will appear
- You can use this feature to play only audio from video or play only video removing audio

### Cursor effects

- You can highlight your cursor movements of camtasia if original screen recording is done using camtasia
- you can use this effect when making tutorial which involve some complex mouse clicking

### Color Themes

- If you like brand specific colors in your video you can set up specific colors for your brands
- File>Manage themes

### Markers

- Use marker to bookmark specific positions in video
- Ctrl+M

### Watermarks in Video

- We can just drop our logo on canvas and position it however we want, most people prefer it on right bottom
- Additional effects
    - remove background color if it has any
    - Increase opacity

### Jump Cut Editing

- so this is very basic concept when recording video, so make sure that when your recording video make sure to take pauses in between, if you make mistake repeat that part again without  stopping this will make your recording happen in single go and it's going to easy to edit bad part later on

### Intro and Outro

- Create Intro and Outro once which represent your brand and you can just drag and drop same item for every video as per requirement
